    "However, the complicated AI model faces several implementation problems.",
    "On the one hand, it needs more time to tune the enormous number of parameters, hindering its use in real-time scenarios.",
    "On the other hand, sufficient training data may not be available in some practical cases, which increases the risk of overfitting.",
